message.body: Alrighty, my darling. Time for werk. Hows your evening going?
Going good. Watched running man and now I'm going my microbio homework I forgot about! HAH! I'm sorry you're at work!
Let it snow let it snow let it snow!
I love you!!!! Going to bed now!
Good morning, darling lovely :) Sorry i didnt text last night. Was super busy. Hope you get to stay inside today, cozy and happy! Love you!!
Hehe. I'm at the library. Haha. I've been here since 8 and I'll stay until 1:24. At that time I'll hop on the train and go home!!!!!
Reaaally?? They cancelled and my baby is still being super productive? You is amazing! Couldnt do it haha.
They didn't cancel :( I'm only being productive because I got a ride to villanova. Hahahaha
Oh haha. Well then. Yik. But no worries. You'll be home before you know it. And then under the blanket on the couch!
Yes!!! Plus hopefully no classes tomorrow will be pretty nice. And I'll use all that time to study (womp womp...no I won't) and I'll be ready for my exam on Thursday!
Haha fingers crossed for no class! And you'll rock it. No sweat :) Not getting any winter action here...just sleety junk. No help. Just gross
Hahaha. I hear Wayne is currently in a blizzard warning. I'm jealous.
Haha yeah theyre supposed to get walloped. Doggies are ready haha. And you'll get plenty :) There will be enough to get rid of school for a day
I want 2 days!!!!!
Hahaha. Jk. I'll be grateful for whatever I get.
Ah greedy woman!! But i hear ya haha. That would be sooo nice. Good luck haha. Like you said. Let it snow, let it snow, let it snow!!!
:D I love you! Have a good night baby!
Haha oh no. Im with you today. Daytime schedule :-p Couldnt sleep again. So...f it, im up.
Hahaha. Whoa!!! I wouldn't be able to do that. I'd be done.
Haha suuure you could. We'll try it one day...for a good reason. Like a vacation haha. But im sure i'll smack a wall of sleepy in the afternoon
Hahaha. Probably! I like it! I wanna go on vacation with you! I have the best times when I'm on vacay with you. Seriously. Whenever I think about times we spent just you and me, I get giddy.
Haha i like it! I like giddy you :) And i live for those times haha. Lets do it again :)
Yeah yeah! Yeah yeah! I can't wait!
Meee neither!! Keep yo summa dresses and bathing suits ready :) Or your english lady outfits...those just might be handy
Haha. I wish!!! Gotta be classy like kate Middleton. I'm not there yet! But I wanna buy another bathing suit. I like the one I saw online!!! I wanna buy it!
Oh hell yes you are. Kate Middletons got nothing on you. And im sure that bathing suit you saw was lovely haha
MUAHAHAHA. I'm gonna be the queen on bathing suits!
In my world, you already are. Bathing suits, maxis, sweats, t shirts. Queen.
Haha. I like how sweats are in that mix.
Hehe those are important :-p You a hottie in dem
Haha. You're cute. I lobe you!
Ohhh. That's a new one. I lobe you. Haha
Oh geee wiz. I lobe you too!

This idiot on the train just put my $20 on the ticket clip and walked away. So I took it off because I didn't want someone to just take it. This freaking jerkoff just scolded me for taking the money off. He then proceeded to tell me to put it back and walked away again. Wtf is up with that?! I'm seriously biting my tongue to a point where I think it might be bleeding.
Ah jeez baby, get outta there. Dumbasses. Hope that got resolved. Get home darling. Please please
It did...but...it was a little embarrassing :(
Sorry baby :-( Dont let it bother you. Ignore it. Im in class right now tho, i call ya when i get out! I love you, so much
I love you!
They keep lessening the snow totals. Doesn't make me optimistic about having off tomorrow :( Not they're saying 4-10 inches :(
